channel.title: Error connecting
channel.description: I'm having error's connecting to my server, and don't know why. I've port forwarded, I have a no-IP, I have the Environmental variables set, I have the newest JDK installed, and I have a working source. I just don't know what's wrong. When I configure/run my server, it says its up, but I doesn't look that way when I try to log in. Anyone willing to have a little conversation with me to see whats wrong, I'd appreciate it. Thanks.
